254
0:13:37.896,000 --> 0:13:41,000
and that's because combatting climate change by capturing carbon

255
0:13:42.693,000 --> 0:13:44,000
isn't just about saving a polar bear

256
0:13:44.775,000 --> 0:13:45,000
or a glacier.

257
0:13:45.965,000 --> 0:13:46,000
It's about saving human lives.

258
0:13:49.905,000 --> 0:13:54,000
A synthetic forest may not ever be as pretty as a real one,

259
0:13:54.946,000 --> 0:13:57,000
