260
0:13:58.589,000 --> 0:13:59,000
but all of the people

261
0:14:00.073,000 --> 0:14:02,000
that we love and cherish,

262
0:14:02.467,000 --> 0:14:06,000
as well as all of our future generations

263
0:14:07.153,000 --> 0:14:08,000
and modern civilization.

264
0:14:08.839,000 --> 0:14:09,000
Thank you.

